861
01:53:28,007 --> 01:53:29,344
- Perbaiki. 
- Sedang kucoba.

861
01:53:29,345 --> 01:53:31,344
Ada yang lihat John?

862
01:53:31,344 --> 01:53:34,221
Pyro? Di mana dia?

863
